WEBVTT

00:01:28.800 --> 00:01:32.190
So he decided to raise her as a boy.

00:01:32.950 --> 00:01:34.403
At three months old,

00:01:34.427 --> 00:01:39.926
she went from being
a baby girl, to baby boy.

00:01:39.950 --> 00:01:42.502
She is given a boy's getup.

00:01:42.526 --> 00:01:45.323
She is allowed to go outside

00:01:45.347 --> 00:01:47.676
and get an education alongside boys.

00:01:47.700 --> 00:01:49.891
She is free, she is confident.

00:01:51.506 --> 00:01:57.674
She observes, she notes
small, everyday injustices

00:01:57.698 --> 00:02:01.603
faced by women and girls in her village.